<ol>
  <li>
    <p>Weather<br />
 Did you know you can check weather forecast of any city from terminal? With this command you can. Your terminal will suggest if you should take umbrella to work today or not ;)</p>

    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code> curl http://wttr.in/pokhara 
</code></pre></div>    </div>
    <p><img src="/img/weather.png" alt="" /></p>
